      "instruction": "<p>Bash your <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, remove the <strong>tough outer layer[s] </strong>and discard, then chop your <strong>softer inner core[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>shallot[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and chop in half and strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Add the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>garlic and</strong> <strong>shallot</strong>, <strong>lemongrass</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>mint leaves </strong>and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until finely chopped – this is your <strong>lemongrass</strong> <strong>paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
