      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once blitzed, combine the<strong> lemongrass paste </strong>with your <strong>vegan burger patty[ies]</strong> in a large bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lemongrass burger mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
