        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>lemongrass burger mix</strong> and shape into 1 patty per person</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> patty[ies] </strong>to the pan and cook for 5 min on each side or until browned, crisp and cooked through – these are your <strong>lemongrass patty[ies]</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
