          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the patty[ies] cooks, peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p><p>Add the <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and give everything a good mix up and set aside – these are your <strong>quick-pickled carrot ribbons</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onions</strong></p>",
