    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> to a baking tray (cut side up) and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until  hot and crusty</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Use 2 trays!</p>",
