    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the base of the <strong>toasted ciabatta</strong> with some <strong>sweet chilli mayo</strong>, the <strong>remaining coriander </strong>and <strong>mint</strong>, a<strong> lemongrass patty </strong>and the <strong>quick-pickled carrot ribbons</strong>, then top with the <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>lemongrass veggie burger </strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips</strong> to the side and drizzle over the <strong>remaining sweet chilli mayo</strong>, then top with the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
